description:
This is a 14 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Pelvic Floor Relaxation | FemFusion Fitness' from the channel Dr. Bri's Vibrant Pelvic Health.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Relax and release pelvic tension with this short guided meditation. Perfect for anyone with pelvic pain or pelvic floor dysfunction; also ideal for ANYONE who carries stress in their pelvic region (hint: that's most of us). Use this is as often as DAILY for an easy way to unwind and connect with your core.
